===Verb===
'''shotgun'''

# {{slang}} As in smoking herbal substance; to inhale from a pipe or other smoking device, followed shortly by an exhalation into someone else’s mouth.

===Transitive Verb===
'''shotgun'''

# {{baseball}} To hit the ball directly back at the pitcher.

